




Given the API Documentation described here : https://github.com/vdespa/introduction-to-postman-course/blob/main/simple-books-api.md


1) create a scenario that verify the creation of token after an authentication.
2) create a scenario that verify that 'type' filter works correctly  on the list of books endpoint (check the case 'fiction' and 'non-fiction')
3) create a tests that verify the successful creation of an order with an available book (book in stock)
4) create a test that verify the unsuccessful creation of order when the book is out of stock.
5) implement html reporting


